Comment: The original description of 
<taxonomicName id="59F84D59927FFFF4FD59FDEDFCF71205" authorityName="ASSING" authorityYear="2009" box="[644,747,578,600]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Orphnebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="110" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scissus">
