</taxonomicName>
is based on a unique male from the Gaoligong Shan (
<bibRefCitation id="FA694B2B927FFFF4FE47FDF0FC371228" author="ASSING V" box="[410,555,607,629]" pageId="9" pageNumber="110" pagination="201 - 226" refId="ref13153" refString="ASSING V. (2009): New species and additional records of Lomechusini from the Palaearctic region (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Aleocharinae). - Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde Serie A, Neue Serie 2: 201 - 226." type="journal article" year="2009">ASSING 2009</bibRefCitation>
). No significant external differences between the above female and the 
<typeStatus id="41438878927FFFF4FE4DFDD3FFF512CF" box="[400,489,636,658]" pageId="9" pageNumber="110">holotype</typeStatus>
were found suggesting that they should represent different species.
</paragraph>
